{"tid":1725322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係鏡頭前做野，除左開遮 ，仲要說明原因","createTime":"2019-11-15T17:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T16:55:33.000Z","uid":213898,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30a846fda4f195b59533f0d27156846f9c23599a","tid":1725322,"uid":213898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"幾個月前有手足都提過，係呢到再提醒下大家。<br />\n好多五毛/外國奶共派用某片段只強調藍絲被圍毆，洗到一部分人腦，又要手足事後大量文宣解釋。係鏡頭前說明原因有好大實際作用：<br />\n<br />\n1.避免對家用黎做假新聞：相信大家見唔少看圖作故事同Cut頭尾既片，邊做野邊大嗌原因，例如「佢斬人呀！」記者報個陣加埋字幕，可避免對家造假<br />\n2.減低Cctvb播放：如果邊搞cctvb邊嗌「造假新聞呀拿！袁x偉奶共狗！」，你估片條會唔會播出街<br />\n3.另類文宣：「林鄭賣港」，「殺人填命」，「毛澤東萬歲」<br />\n<br />\n口才好手足可以用埋外語"},{"pid":"1f67ce058989afe4cc260d49f0425fc36b847631","tid":1725322,"uid":119454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T19:48:05.000Z","msg":"定策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467881f1501b2aea94e0b8e4517f2405d0f2a6f0","tid":1725322,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T19:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36d120b8bac15dea3ad1682058c8eb8faa12ce0","tid":1725322,"uid":152809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:27:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a649286022e2a45f120a83a552ae01c65b8446d","tid":1725322,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJ2QEMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJ2QEMQ.jpg&h=55f2d382&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"545431d42d0db511f99111be023656eabe20ea15","tid":1725322,"uid":213898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a649286022e2a45f120a83a552ae01c65b8446d","tid":1725322,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T20:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJ2Q